chance of a lifetime is a 1991 television film .   it stars betty white , leslie nielsen , and ed begley , jr . .   the romance-comedy movie follows a woman named evelyn ( played by betty white ) who receives news from her doctor that she only has 6 months to live .   she sets off on a vacation to mexico where she meets a man named lloyd ( leslie nielson ) , and the two fall in love .   the pair are both widowers and spend time " learning to live again " , but evelyn soon finds out that her original diagnosis was wrong .   faced with the fact that she has longer than 6 months , evelyn has to decide whether she wants to stay in a relationship with lloyd .